				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				WOW! Even funner than the last post I read.<BR>
<BR>
First, If you're NOT of age or sense to use or understand this spell then SHUT UP!  Post on the newbie board.  This is an upgrade to our AoE Lightning spell that does around 185 damage to 4 mobs at a time.  Great spell for Quad kiting in OT.  But DL is a different story.  The mobs have WAY more HP and you run just short to actually kill all 4 off in one round.  This spell will definitely do the trick at 477 damage.  Quad that and you've got 1908 damage for 240 mana.  NOT BAD!<BR>
I'm not sure if we can kite more than 4 with this upgrade yet, but I'll find out soon enough.<BR>
<BR>
As for this other nonsense, I can't believe the ignorance.  Druids and Necro's can solo into their 50's.  DOH - &quot;SAY IT AINT SO&quot;.  &quot;IT IS - IT IS - IT IS SO&quot;.  We do it OUTDOORS and it's somewhat boring.  That's why we group.  And as said below we ALWAYS group in dungeons.  We're not made for dungeons.<BR>
<BR>
As for experience, we get far better experience Solo or partnered, and don't go spouting off about group bonuses.  If a mob gives 1000 exp points solo and you have 6 in a group giving 50% bonus I get 250 exp.  Hmmmm.  &quot;But we kill mo faster&quot;, SO.  I can kill ONE in less time than it takes a group to Kill 6 and get ALL the exp and loot.  Especially when there's a LOVELY chanter nearby.  <BR>
<BR>
Love your character and have fun.<BR>

